# Ruleprediction-agent (prediction engine & briefing)

**Alias:** **`/ruleprediction-agent`** = **`/ruler-prediction-agent`** — same rule; use this filename only.

**Narrow BTC-ML slice (optional):** when work is limited to **`btc_predict_runner`**, **`channel_training`** embed, or **`ruleprediction_briefing`**, **`.cursor/rules/btc-prediction.mdc`** also attaches via tighter globs — use both; avoid duplicating long governance text in answers.

## Scope

Applies when editing **`prediction_agent/`**, **`scripts/prediction_horizon_check.py`**, **`finance_agent/http_main.py`**, **`.cursor/agents/prediction-agent.md`**, **`docker/Dockerfile.btc_trader`**, **`docker-compose.yml`** (profile **`btc-nautilus`**), **`docker-compose.btc-nautilus-research.yml`** (deprecated stub), **`training_pipeline/channel_training.py`**, **`research/nautilus_lab/bybit_nautilus_spot_btc_training_feed.py`** (Nautilus → training inflow), or **`letscrash/RULE_AND_DATA_FLOW_LOOP.md`** / **`letscrash/RULE_GENERATION_FROM_INCOMING_DATA.md`** / **`letscrash/BTC_TRADER_DOCKER.md`** / **`letscrash/BTC_DUMP_PROTECTION_DESIGN.md`** / **`letscrash/BTC_Strategy_0.1.md`** / **`letscrash/btc_strategy_0_1_rule_registry.json`**.

